ABOUT OPTIFIT PERFORM

OPTIFIT APPROACH

Our approach follows a scientific-backed model from the National Academy of Sports Medicine. It allows everyone to follow an evidence-based integrated program built with your goal in mind, regardless if you are a high-performing athlete, or someone starting out in their fitness journey. Alongside that, you will be supported by our coaching practice and we will make sure together that you will stay on track and make sure you get results.

Make sure to reach out to us and we will provide you with the guidance you need to become the best version of yourself. Let's make it happen today!

MEET THE TRAINER

NASM CPT ANDREI TRANDAFIR

NASM Certified Personal Trainer and Nutrition Coach, Andrei has a background in Organisational Psychology with extensive practice in amateur, as well as professional competitions in sports such as football, tennis and martial arts. His focus is on developing a well-rounded, balanced and strong body-mind connection that supports your overall well-being. Some of the training tools in his repertoire that will help you reach your goals include resistance training, speed-agility-quickness training, plyo-metric (reactive) training, balance & core strengthening exercises, as well as a holistic approach to nutrition.

NASM CPT & NUTRITION COACH INTERNATIONAL LICENSEE

MSC. ORGANIZATIONAL PSYCHOLOGY

ACTIVE IN FOOTBALL, TENNIS, MARTIAL ARTS AND ENDURANCE SPORTS
